Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Singapore%20last%20year%20to%20pursue%20my%20MBA%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20(NUS).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20going%20to%20business%20school%2C%20I'd%20graduated%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%20Boulder%20with%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20aerospace%20engineering%20with%20a%20minor%20in%20biology%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduation%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flockheed-martin-shares-fall-pentagon-f35-requests-air-force-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELockheed%20Martin%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20starting%20my%20own%20business.%20That%20was%20when%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20theoretical%20underpinnings%20of%20business.%20Getting%20an%20MBA%20felt%20like%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20applying%20to%20several%20business%20schools%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-into-insead-business-school-mba-program-consulting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EINSEAD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwharton-business-school-upenn-ai-curriculum-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWharton%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-salaries-stanford-mba-graduates-industries-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStanford%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcambridge-university-library-crowned-britains-best-new-building-riba-stirling-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECambridge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20received%20offers%20from%20INSEAD%20and%20NUS%2C%20and%20picked%20NUS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae4b1261-53ae-426f-a6bc-e743c06420c4%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20may%20be%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20MBA%2C%20but%20international%20schools%20offer%20something%20different%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20knows%20that%20the%20US%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20MBA.%20When%20people%20think%20about%20getting%20an%20MBA%2C%20they%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20you%20go%20to%20a%20US%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20wasn't%20what%20I%20wanted%20from%20my%20MBA%20journey.%20I%20wanted%20a%20unique%20experience%20for%20myself.%20That%20drove%20me%20to%20consider%20international%20schools%20instead.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20surrounded%20by%20people%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20to%20challenge%20myself%20intellectually%20and%20culturally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20you%20can%20get%20diversity%20from%20attending%20a%20US%20business%20school.%20Those%20programs%20do%20try%20to%20attract%20foreign%20students%20as%20well%2C%20but%20the%20experience%20just%20isn't%20the%20same.%20You%20will%20get%20to%20meet%20people%20from%20different%20countries%2C%20but%20you%20won't%20get%20to%20engage%20with%20their%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EINSEAD%20does%20have%20a%20campus%20in%20Singapore%2C%20but%20I%20found%20NUS%20to%20be%20more%20integrated%20with%20the%20country.%20It%20felt%20a%20lot%20more%20community-driven%2C%20was%20affordable%2C%20and%20also%20well-rated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e534d449-6443-4f21-9c4d-579f67ef1226%5C%22%3EThe%20fact%20that%20I%20can%20jump%20on%20a%20plane%20and%20go%20anywhere%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%20is%20unbelievable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryan%20Wall%20(third%20from%20left)%20celebrating%20Diwali%20with%20his%20classmates%20from%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684bd915f748d8c055f3a174%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWall%20(third%20from%20left)%20is%20the%20president%20of%20the%20business%20school's%20cultural%2C%20social%2C%20and%20community%20club.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Wall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20a