%20speaking%20at%20the%20Monte-Carlo%20TV%20Festival%20on%20Monday%2C%20Wright%20opened%20up%20about%20fighting%20for%20equal%20pay%20with%20Spacey%20going%20into%20the%20fourth%20season%20of%20the%20hit%20Netflix%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20difficult%2C%20I%20am%20going%20to%20be%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Frobin-wright-house-of-cards-not-paying-same-kevin-spacey-1236432728%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Variety%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20said%2C%20'I%20think%20it's%20only%20fair%20because%20my%20character%20became%20as%20popular%20as%20%5BSpacey's%5D%2C'%20they%20said%2C%20'We%20can't%20pay%20you%20the%20same%20as%20an%20actor%2C%20so%20we%20will%20make%20you%20exec%20producer%20and%20you%20can%20direct.%20We%20will%20give%20you%20three%20different%20paychecks.'%20I%20asked%2C%20'Why%20can't%20you%20pay%20me%20as%20an%20actor%3F'%20'Because%20you%20didn't%20win%20an%20Academy%20Award.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Claire%20Underwood%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a71e11c7e7a351e008b4c6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERobin%20Wright%20played%20Claire%20Underwood%20on%20the%20Netflix%20series%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20Cards.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20landmark%20Netflix%20series%20about%20amoral%20politician%20Frank%20Underwood%20(Spacey)%20and%20his%20ambitious%20wife%20Claire%20(Wright)%20debuted%20in%202013%2C%20Spacey%20was%20an%20established%20star%20who%20had%20already%20won%20two%20Oscars%3A%20best%20supporting%20actor%20for%201995's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Usual%20Suspects%26quot%3B%20and%20best%20actor%20for%201999's%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Beauty.%26quot%3B%20A%20year%20later%20in%202014%2C%20he%20was%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%